This software and associated data may be viewed and forked for 
transparency purposes only. Use of this code is subject to the 
following restrictions:

YOU MAY NOT:
- Replicate or repurpose this code to scrape, track, or monitor 
  incarcerated or formerly incarcerated individuals.
- Use this code or data to build any database linking individuals 
  to periods of incarceration.
- Share, publish, or sell any decrypted personal data obtained 
  through this tool.
- Use this code or data for any law enforcement, immigration 
  enforcement, or government surveillance purpose.
- Use this code or data for any commercial purpose.

Violation of these terms is strictly prohibited.
For research or data inquiries, contact eappelson@laaclu.org
